com.k2.Expressions.expression

Class ExpressionBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.k2.Expressions.expression.ExpressionBuilder

  • public class ExpressionBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    The expression builder provides factory methods to create implementations of the Expression interface that provide known functions

      • locate

        public Expression<java.lang.Integer> locate(Expression<java.lang.String> string,
                                            Expression<java.lang.String> pattern)
        Create an expression to return the location of one string in another or 0 if the pattern is not contained in the string
        Parameters:
        string - The expression providing the string in which to search for the pattern
